            "en": "<h3><strong>Payment</strong></h3><p>The employer receives the recruitment incentive in <strong>two instalments</strong>:</p><ul><li>a first instalment of maximum EUR 1,250, when the employee has worked for the company for three months</li><li>a second instalment of maximum EUR 3,000, when the employee has worked for the company for one year.</li></ul><h3><strong>Part-time employment</strong></h3><ul><li>If the employee works less than 30%, no subsidy will be granted.</li><li>If the employee works between 30% and 80%, the subsidy will be 60% of the maximum (EUR 750 for the first instalment and EUR 1,800 for the second).</li><li>If the employee works more than 80%, the employer will receive the maximum subsidy.</li></ul><p>The first subsidies have been paid since 10 October 2017.</p>"
